sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy-based Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker Proxy<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant BBR as Body-Based Router<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>(vLLM/SGLang/TRT-LLM)
    participant LatencyPred as Latency Prediction<br/>8001/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 1: Inference Request Routing (EPP)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (Gateway-enforced)
    Gateway->>EPP: gRPC ExternalProcessor.Process<br/>9002/TCP, TLS (self-signed)<br/>Bidirectional stream

    Note over EPP: Parse request body (OpenAI/vLLM/passthrough)<br/>Evaluate InferenceModelRewrite rules<br/>Apply weighted traffic splitting

    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods, CRDs<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Pod endpoints + CRD state

    EPP->>ModelServer: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP (configurable port)<br/>Auth: None
    ModelServer-->>EPP: queue_depth, kv_cache_usage,<br/>running_requests, lora_info

    opt Latency Prediction Enabled
        EPP->>LatencyPred: POST /predict/bulk/strict<br/>HTTP/8001, plaintext<br/>TTFT/TPOT estimation
        LatencyPred-->>EPP: Predicted latencies
    end

    Note over EPP: Scheduling Framework:<br/>Filter → Score → Pick optimal endpoint<br/>Flow Control: Priority queue + admission

    EPP-->>Gateway: gRPC response<br/>Selected endpoint address<br/>Rewritten model name (if applicable)
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 or gRPC<br/>plaintext (internal)
    ModelServer-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 2: Body-Based Routing (BBR)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>BBR: gRPC ExternalProcessor.Process<br/>9004/TCP, TLS (self-signed)<br/>Bidirectional stream

    Note over BBR: Extract body fields (model name)<br/>Inject as HTTP headers<br/>LoRA adapter mapping lookup

    BBR-->>Gateway: gRPC response<br/>Header mutations<br/>(X-Gateway-Model-Name, etc.)
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward with injected headers<br/>Route based on header values
    ModelServer-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 3: Metrics Scraping (Background)

    loop Every 50ms (configurable)
        EPP->>ModelServer: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)<br/>InsecureSkipVerify=true (default)
        ModelServer-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics<br/>queue depth, KV cache, LoRA status
        Note over EPP: Update in-memory datastore<br/>Feed scheduling decisions
    end
